ashzone header settings\" />',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2008/12/29/crashzone-new-feature-work-sheet/','2008-12-29 04:01:03','2008-12-29 04:01:03',NULL),(1201,'Crashzone new feature - email autocomplete','crashzone-new-feature-email-autocomplete','Crashzone new feature - email autocomplete','<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/crashzone-email-autocomplete.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone email autocomplete\" />\r\n\r\nEmail address autocomplete is a useful tool that will make it even easier to email quotes from Crashzone.\r\n<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/crashzone-email-autocomplete-insurance-section.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone email autocomplete insurance section\" />\r\nEmail autocomplete will list any email address that has been entered previously in the insurance field from the details page.',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2008/12/31/crashzone-new-feature-email-autocomplete/','2008-12-31 02:03:46','2008-12-31 02:03:46',NULL),(1204,'Crashzone new feature - emails saved in notes','crashzone-new-feature-emails-saved-in-notes','Crashzone new feature - emails saved in notes',' <img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/crashzone-email-saved-in-notes1.JPG\" alt=\"Crashzone emails saved in notes\" />\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/crashzone-email-notes.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone email saved in notes\" />\r\nWhen you email a quote from the Crashzone system a new note will be added in the details page along with a copy of the email sent. The note shows the time and date that the email was sent and if you click on view it will show the quote in PDF format.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/crashzone-email-quote-in-notes.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone email quote in notes\" />\r\n\r\nEmails saved in notes allows you to accurately track your quotes that have been emailed from Crashzone.',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/01/05/crashzone-new-feature-emails-saved-in-notes/','2009-01-05 03:39:27','2009-01-05 03:39:27',NULL),(1208,'Crashzone meets with the MTAWA','crashzone-meets-with-the-mtawa','Crashzone meets with the MTAWA','<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/mtawa.jpg\" alt=\"MTAWA\" />\r\n<p align=\"left\">A big thank you to Ian &amp; Marie from the MTAWA for taking time out of their busy schedule to meet with Crashzone. It is great to see that there is an organisation out there looking after the best interests of the smash repair industry. For more information about the MTAWA please visit their website <a href=\"http://www.mtawa.com.au/\">http://www.mtawa.com.au/</a></p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/01/08/crashzone-meets-with-the-mtawa/','2009-01-08 02:49:06','2009-01-08 02:49:06',NULL),(1210,'Crashzone settings page - show note','crashzone-settings-page-show-note','Crashzone settings page - show note',' <img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/crashzone-notes.JPG\" alt=\"Crashzone notes\" />\r\n<p align=\"left\">If you don\'t see notes in the details page you will need to activate the note feature from the settings page.</p>\r\n<em>* Click on the settings page link  ( located top right of the screen )\r\n* Click on the Show note Tick box\r\n* Scroll down to the bottom of the settings page and click submit</em>  \r\n\r\n <img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/crashzone-show-notes1.JPG\" alt=\"Crashzone settings page show note\" />',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/01/09/crashzone-settings-page-show-note/','2009-01-09 04:36:59','2009-01-09 04:36:59',NULL),(1215,'Ariana Accident Repair Centre - Cannington repairer','ariana-accident-repair-centre-cannington-repairer','Ariana Accident Repair Centre - Cannington repairer','<strong>Ariana Accident Repair Centre</strong>\r\n\r\n43 Hogarth Street Cannington 6107 WA\r\nPh: (08) 9356 6855\r\nFax:  (08) 9356 6844\r\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:arianasmash@bigpond.com\">arianasmash@bigpond.com</a>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/ariana-smash-repairs-map.JPG\" alt=\"Ariana Smash Repairs map\" />',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/01/27/ariana-accident-repair-centre-cannington-repairer/','2009-01-27 03:34:56','2014-04-15 05:28:13',NULL),(1217,'Crashzone new feature - backup','crashzone-new-feature-backup','Crashzone new feature - backup','Great news, you can now backup your quotes from Crashzone \r\n\r\n<em>* Click on the settings link to access the settings page\r\n* Scroll down to the backup section in the settings page\r\n* Enter the  quote range for the backup ( quote number \"From\" \"To\" )\r\n* Click on \"Zip\" to generate the backup\r\n* When the backup is complete you will receive an email  with a link to download\r\n* Download load the backup from your email</em>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/crashzone-backup.JPG\" alt=\"Crashzone backup\" />\r\n* Please note that depending on the size of the backup it make take several minutes to generate and download the backup.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/crashzone-backup-email1.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone backup email\" />',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/01/12/crashzone-new-feature-backup/','2009-01-12 03:22:30','2009-01-12 03:22:30',NULL),(1221,'Crashzone new feature - blank letterhead','crashzone-new-feature-blank-letterhead','Crashzone new feature - blank letterhead',' <img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/crashzone-blank-letterhead-example.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone blank letterhead example\" />\r\n\r\nBlank letterhead is for customers that prefer to use their own stationary when printing. This feature allow you print a blank letterhead, but still e