ry.  Training will run from 9am at John Hunter Car Repairs, located at 47 Greek Street Glebe NSW 2037. Training will be provided on a one on one basis and is a good opportunity for both existing and new customers. for more information or to RSVP please contact <a href=\"mailto:support@crashzone.com.au\">support@crashzone.com.au</a> or phone 1300 721 090</p>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/01/29/crashzone-training-day-07022009/','2009-01-29 05:40:19','2009-01-29 05:40:19',NULL),(1265,'Crashzone - changing your quote and invoice number','crashzone-changing-your-quote-and-invoice-number','Crashzone - changing your quote and invoice number','From the settings page in Crashzone you can set the starting point for your quotes and invoices.\r\n\r\n <img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/02/crashzone-set-our-ref-inv-no.JPG\" alt=\"Crashzone set our ref &amp; Invoice Number\" />\r\n\r\n* From any page in Crashzone click on the settings link\r\n* Enter the \"Our ref from\"  (quote number you want to start from)\r\n* Enter the \"Invoice from\" ( Invoice number you want to start from)\r\n* Click submit to save the changes\r\n\r\nThe next quote created will have the new quote number.',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/02/04/crashzone-changing-your-quote-and-invoice-number/','2009-02-04 06:33:06','2009-02-04 06:33:06',NULL),(1267,'Crashzone training video - how to setup ARNIE','crashzone-training-video-how-to-setup-arnie','Crashzone training video - how to setup ARNIE','<object width=\"425\" height=\"344\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/b2fIEAX2tPQ&hl=en&fs=1\"></param><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\"></param><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\"></param><embed src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/b2fIEAX2tPQ&hl=en&fs=1\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"425\" height=\"344\"></embed></object>\r\n\r