zone pick list items\" />\r\n<p align=\"left\">Crashzone will update the standard choice list soon, and we would like to invite our customers to have an input for the new list. If there are any items you think should be added or edited please email them to support@crashzone.com.au or fax: 02 8569 0319</p>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/06/16/crashzone-choice-list-update/','2009-06-16 10:07:56','2009-06-16 10:07:56',NULL),(1546,'How to send a quote to ARNIE','how-to-send-a-quote-to-arnie','How to send a quote to ARNIE','<object width=\"425\" height=\"344\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/NN3FNs2VmmU&hl=en&fs=1&\"></param><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\"></param><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\"></param><embed src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/NN3FNs2VmmU&hl=en&fs=1&\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"425\" height=\"344\"></embed></object>\r\n\r\n* Once the quote is written and ready to send go to the details page\r\n* Complete all mandatory fields in the details page\r\n* Click on the ARNIE button to send the quote to ARNIE \r\n* A new note will be added to the bottom of the details page to confirm that the quote has been sent to ARNIE\r\n* ARNIE will send an email to confirm the quote has been received from Crashzone\r\n* ARNIE will send back the adjusted quote/Authority to your email address\r\n* when the job has been completed press create tax invoice to generate the invoice \r\n* Click on the ARNIE button to send the invoice to ARNIE \r\n* A new note will be added to the bottom of the details page to confirm that the invoice has been sent to ARNIE\r\n* ARNIE will send an email to confirm the invoice has been received from Crashzone\r\n* Once approved ARNIE will email back the payment authority to your email address  \r\n\r\nPlease visit the Crashzone help page to download the complete ARNIE/Crashzone user manual.',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/06/19/how-to-send-a-quote-to-arnie/','2009-06-19 01:26:07','2009-06-19 01:26:07',NULL),(1549,'Betta Body Repairs - Southport repairer','betta-body-repairs-southport-repairer-2','Betta Body Repairs - Southport repairer','<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/betta-body-repairs.jpg\" alt=\"Betta Body Repairs\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Betta Body Repairs</strong>\r\nBrett Smith\r\n2/2 Case St Southport QLD 4215\r\nPh: 07 5591 6131\r\nFax: 07 5591 6132\r\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:brettsmith12@bigpond.com\">brettsmith12@bigpond.com</a>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/betta-body-repairs-map.jpg\" alt=\"Betta Body Repairs map\" />',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/06/22/betta-body-repairs-southport-repairer-2/','2009-06-22 01:54:10','2009-06-22 01:54:10',NULL),(1550,'How much extra will your quoting systems supplier charge you to let you do quoting??','how-much-extra-will-your-quoting-systems-supplier-charge-you-to-let-you-do-quoting','How much extra will your quoting systems supplier charge you to let you do quoting??',' <img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/crashzone-quote-on-mazda-rx8.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone quote on Mazda RX8\" />\r\n\r\n<u>Some quoting system suppliers are charging up to $30,000 installation charge plus an additional ongoing support fee of $250/month to enable Quoting for their customers.</u>\r\n\r\n<strong>Crashzone customers pay no extra to use the quoting - it is included in the standard feature.</strong>\r\n\r\nCrashzone were first to have a quoting system capable of quoting for free and have over 100 satisfied customers currently  doing quotes - and none of these customers is paying any additional fees to be able to use the NTAR style.\r\n\r\nCrashzone users can enable Quoting by simply signing up from the Crashzone website, no site visit or installation is required. Once users have done the sign up they can create quotes immediately using Crashzone online documentation icon <a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/help/Crashzone-NTAR-manual.pdf\">(click here to read)</a> or users can call the Crashzone help desk on <strong>1800 721 090.</strong>\r\n\r\nAs well Crashzone offer free training for all users at our training centers.\r\n\r\nBefore you pay your current software provider a large fee to \"upgrade\" to have quoting, contact Crashzone for a free demonstration and a quote. We think you will be pleasantly surprised at the features and the price  - FREE',0,0,3,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/07/06/how-much-extra-will-your-quoting-systems-supplier-charge-you-to-let-you-do-quoting/','2009-07-06 08:49:04','2009-07-07 04:46:15',NULL),(1552,'Crashzone at Wetherill Park TAFE','crashzone-at-wetherill-park-tafe','Crashzone at Wetherill Park TAFE','<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/wetherill-park-tafe.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone at Wetherill Park TAFE\" />\r\n\r\nCrashzone at Wetherill Park TAFE doing training with the stage 3 students. With Crashzone each student can have their own system that they can use in the class room and at home.',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/06/24/crashzone-at-wetherill-park-tafe/','2009-06-24 01:48:43','2009-06-24 01:48:43',NULL),(1554,'Crashzone - customer survey','crashzone-customer-survey','Crashzone - customer survey',' <img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/lamborghini.jpg\" alt=\"Yellow lamborghini\" />\r\n\r\nDear valued Crashzone customer, please help us by completing the attached customer survey. If you could please fill out the attached sheet and fax it back to us ( Fax: 02 8569 0319 ) at your earliest convenience. Your feedback would be greatly appreciated.\r\n\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" /><meta name=\"ProgId\" content=\"Word.Document\" /><meta name=\"Generator\" content=\"