ond big bill\" />\r\n\r\nA Telstra BigPond customer has been slugged thousands of dollars for excess data usage and others have been hit with unexpected bills for downloads they claim they didn\'t use. To read the full article please visit<a href=\"http://www.smh.com.au/technology/biz-tech/bill-shock-bigpond-users-charged-thousands-for-data-they-didnt-use-20090624-cw6b.html\"> smh.com.au\r\n</a>\r\n\r\nFor fast reliable ADSL2 consider iinet.com.au\r\n<a href=\"http://iinet.net.au/customers/\"><img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/iinet.jpg\" alt=\"iinet - internet service provider\" /></a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/06/25/telstra-bigpond-over-charged/','2009-06-25 06:10:58','2009-06-25 06:10:58',NULL),(1562,'Chinese made 4WD in Australia','chinese-made-4wd-in-australia','Chinese made 4WD in Australia','<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/gwm-4wd.jpg\" alt=\"Great Wall Motors SA220 ute\" />\r\n<p align=\"left\">The first Chinese-branded cars went on sale in Australia today in the form of two utes from Great Wall Motors. To read the full story please visit <a href=\"http://www.drive.com.au/Editorial/ArticleDetail.aspx?ArticleID=63917&amp;vf=2&amp;pg=1\">smh.com.au</a></p>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/2009/06/26/chinese-made-4wd-in-australia/','2009-06-26 08:55:32','2009-06-26 08:55:32',NULL),(1565,'Burwood Rd Smash Repairs - Burwood repairer','burwood-rd-smash-repairs-burwood-repairer','Burwood Rd Smash Repairs - Burwood repairer',' <img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/burwood-rd-smash-repairs.jpg\" alt=\"Burwood Rd Smash Repairs\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Burwood Rd Smash Repairs</strong>\r\nTony Sciacca\r\n78 Burwood Rd, Burwood Heights NSW 2136\r\nPhone: 02 9747 8110\r\nFax: 02 9744 7558\r\nEmail: burwoodrdsmash@optusnet.com.au\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/06/burwood-rd-smash-repairs-map.jpg\