 add images to the quote','crashzone-%e2%80%93-how-to-add-images-to-the-quote','Crashzone – how to add images to the quote','<div>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"../wp-content/uploads/2009/07/crashzone-adding-images-3.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone - adding images to the quote\" />\r\n\r\nAdding images to your quote is done by email\r\n\r\n* Open a new email\r\n* Type in your Crashzone email address\r\n* Type the Crashzone quote number into the subject i.e ( 5013 )\r\n* Attach images to the email\r\n* Send email\r\n* Images will now attach to the quote  ( the process takes approx 1  minute )\r\n* Click on the details tab to refresh the system and load the new images\r\n\r\n<img src=\"../wp-content/uploads/2009/07/crashzone-images-on-details-page.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone - images on details page\" />\r\n\r\nPlease contact support@crashzone.com.au if you need any help with adding images to Crashzone.\r\n\r\n</div>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=2596','2011-04-01 08:11:18','2011-04-01 08:11:18',NULL),(2600,'Collision Repair Expo 12 - 14 May 2011','collision-repair-expo-12-14-may-2011','Collision Repair Expo 12 - 14 May 2011','<a href=\"../wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Collision-Repair-Expo-2011.jpg\"><img title=\"Collision Repair Expo 2011\" src=\"../wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Collision-Repair-Expo-2011.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"101\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Come along and visit Crashzone at the Collision Repair Expo stand AB45</strong>\r\n\r\nHosted by the Australian Automotive Aftermarket Association (AAAA),    the COLLISION REPAIR EXPO will be held from Thursday 12 – Saturday 14    May 2011 at the Melbourne Exhibition Centre, in conjunction with the    Australian Auto Aftermarket Expo. please visit <a href=\"http://www.collisionrepair.com.au/\">www.collisionrepair.com.au</a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=2600','2011-04-04 05:00:21','2011-04-04 05:00:21',NULL),(2604,'Six-storey car park plunge','six-storey-car-park-plunge','Six-storey