1 08:40:08',NULL),(4282,'Jaguar F-Type: first images, new name confirmed','jaguar-f-type-first-images-new-name-confirmed','Jaguar F-Type: first images, new name confirmed','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/car1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4285\" title=\"car1\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/car1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"316\" /></a>The Jaguar C-X16 concept will go on sale in 2013 with an emotive name  for the new compact two-seater sports car: the Jaguar F-Type.\r\n\r\nBritain’s Indian-owned sports-luxury brand confirmed at today’s 2012 New  York motor show that it would give the sports car a name that makes it a  natural successor to the famous 1960s E-Type.\r\n\r\nFor the full story, please visit <a href=\"http://www.caradvice.com.au/161075/ferrari-f12-berlinetta-the-fastest-ferrari-ever-revealed/\">caradvice.com.au</a>',0,0,1,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4282','2012-04-05 10:09:09','2012-04-05 10:09:09',NULL),(4288,'Crashzone - Your car model is not in the list','crashzone-your-car-model-is-not-in-the-list','Crashzone - Your car model is not in the list','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/57.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4289\" title=\"57\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/57.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"578\" /></a>If you cannot find your car model from the list, please follow the instruction, also the shown picture above\r\n\r\nIn the <strong>Vehicle</strong> section, click <strong>E</strong> button and type in your car model by hand.',0,0,1,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4288','2012-05-06 23:10:04','2012-05-07 02:25:24',NULL),(4298,'Porsche\'s \'purist\' SUV ','porsches-purist-suv','Porsche\'s \'purist\' SUV ','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/porsche-cayenne_600d-600x400.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4301\" title=\"porsche-cayenne_600d-600x400\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/porsche-cayenne_600d-600x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"367\" /></a>More Bathurst or Bondi than bush basher, German brand\'s new Cayenne GTS is one hardcore soft-roader.\r\n\r\nThe new Cayenne GTS is designed to appeal to those who want to go-fast-soft-roader who don\'t plan to go off the beaten track. Ever.\r\n\r\nFor the full story, please visit <a href=\"http://news.drive.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\">news.drive.com.au</a>',0,0,1,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4298','2012-04-12 03:56:33','2012-04-12 04:21:21',NULL),(4309,'2012 Lotus Elise Club Racer launched','2012-lotus-elise-club-racer-launched','2012 Lotus Elise Club Racer launched','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4310\" title=\"1\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"296\" /></a>Lotus is going back to basics with the 2012 <strong>Lotus Elise Club Racer</strong>.\r\n\r\nThe same naturally aspirated 1.6-litre four-cylinder engine remains,  producing an identical 100kW of power at 6000rpm and 160Nm at 4400rpm  supplying drive to the rear wheels via a six-speed manual transmission.  Fuel consumption comes in at 6.3 litres per 100 km.\r\n\r\nFor the full story, please visit <a href=\"http://www.caradvice.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.caradvice.com.au/</a>',0,0,1,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4309','2012-04-19 02:22:04','2012-04-19 02:22:04',NULL),(4323,'Parking fines on Anzac Day ','parking-fines-on-anzac-day','Parking fines on Anzac Day ','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/parking-ticket.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4324\" title=\"parking ticket\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/parking-ticket.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"560\" height=\"251\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThey parked at 4.08am at the Botanic Gardens but misread the signs and,  like at least 10 others, came back to their cars to find they had been  hit with $88 fines. For the full story please visit<a href=\"http://www.news.com.au/features/anzac-day/anger-at-dawn-raid-over-anzac-day-parking/story-e6frfle0-1226340370844\"> news.com.au</a>\r\n<div></div>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4323','2012-04-27 02:54:02','2012-04-27 02:54:02',NULL),(4328,'Auto Transformers - Parafield Gardens repairer','auto-transformers-parafield-gardens-repairer','Auto Transformers - Parafield Gardens repairer','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Auto-Transformers-Workshop.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4329\" title=\"Auto Transformers Workshop\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Auto-Transformers-Workshop.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"262\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Auto Transformers</strong>\r\n\r\n1 / 355 Martins Rd Parafield Gardens SA 5107\r\n<strong>Phone:</strong> 08 8281 6770\r\n<strong>Mobile:</strong> 0400 390 139\r\n<strong>Email:</strong> info@autotransformers.com.au\r\n<strong>Website:</strong> www.autotransformers.com.au\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Auto-Transformers.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4337\" title=\"Auto Transformers\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Auto-Transformers.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"350\" height=\"230\" /></a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4328','2012-05-02 02:45:02','2012-05-02 02:45:02',NULL),(4332,'The cheapest way into the seat of a new Mercedes-Benz','the-cheapest-way-into-the-seat-of-a-new-mercedes-benz','The cheapest way into the seat of a new Mercedes-Benz','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/timthumb.php_.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/timthumb.php_.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"timthumb.php\" width=\"590\" height=\"296\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4333\" /></a>\r\n\r\nGetting comfortable in the seat of your brand-new Mercedes-Benz has just become a whole lot cheaper.\r\n\r\nThe German-based luxury car maker has teamed with the Formitalia Luxury Group, one of the Italy’s leading manufacturers of… designer furniture.\r\n\r\nFor the full story, please visit <a href=\"http://www.caradvice.com.au/170456/the-cheapest-way-into-the-seat-of-a-new-mercedes-benz/\">CarAdvice</a>',0,0,1,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4332','2012-05-01 04:59:32','2012-05-01 04:59:32',NULL),(4342,'All aluminium 2013 Mercedes-Benz SL','all-aluminium-2013-mercedes-benz-sl','All aluminium 2013 Mercedes-Benz SL','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Mercedes-benz2013alumin.gif\"><img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Mercedes-benz2013alumin.gif\" alt=\"\" title=\"Mercedes-benz2013alumin\" width=\"590\" height=\"374\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4343\" /></a>\r\n\r\nMercedes-Benz\'s new SL weighs around 140 kilograms less than its predecessor thanks to a highly ridgid aluminium bodyshell.\r\n\r\nThe new SL is produced almost entirely from aluminium.\r\n\r\nAccording to a story in Collision Week the make up of the bodyshell is: 44 percent cast aluminum, 17 percent aluminum sections, 28 percent aluminum sheet metal, 8 percent steel and 3 percent other materials.\r\n\r\nFor full story, please visit <a href=\"http://www.paintandpanel.com.au\">www.paintandpanel.com.au</a>',0,0,1,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4342','2012-05-03 02:20:21','2012-05-03 02:20:21',NULL),(4348,'Mercedes-Benz plots SUV sales attack for 2014','mercedes-benz-plots-suv-sales-attack-for-2014','Mercedes-Benz plots SUV sales attack for 2014','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/mec.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/mec.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"mec\" width=\"590\" height=\"296\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4349\" /></a>\r\n\r\nMercedes-Benz Australia has warned rivals Audi and BMW that it will become a stronger force in the SUV category once it has two key new 4WD models in showrooms by 2014.\r\n\r\nThe local subsidiary of the German car maker has just launched the third-generation Mercedes-Benz ML in Australia, its competitor for the Audi Q7 and BMW X5 large luxury SUVs.\r\n\r\nA next-generation Mercedes-Benz GL arrives in 2013, along with a facelift of the army-inspired G-Class.\r\n\r\nFor full story, please visit <a href=\"http://www.caradvice.com.au\">www.caradvice.com.au</a>',0,0,1,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4348','2012-05-08 04:05:04','2012-05-08 04:05:04',NULL),(4355,'Aston Martin DBS Ultimate revealed online','aston-martin-dbs-ultimate-revealed-online','Aston Martin DBS Ultimate revealed online','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/aston-martin-dbs-ultimate-1-625x291.png\"><img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/aston-martin-dbs-ultimate-1-625x291.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"aston-martin-dbs-ultimate-1-625x291\" width=\"590\" height=\"275\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-4356\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe Aston Martin DBS Ultimate limited edition has been revealed on the brand’s public website ahead of its launch later this year.\r\n\r\nIf Australian customers get in quick enough, they will be asked to part with $466,100 for the DBS Ultimate coupe Touchtronic II or $497,000 for the DBS Ultimate Volante Touchtronic II (recommended retail prices excluding dealer delivery and on-road costs).',0,0,1,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4355','2012-05-10 02:52:42','2012-05-10 02:52:42',NULL),(4361,'Crashzone free SMS for customers','crashzone-free-sms-for-customers','Crashzone free SMS for customers','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012