rice for an Australian-made car sold at auction. For the full story please visit <a href=\"http://smh.drive.com.au/motor-news/man-bids-900000-for-holden-20130311-2fvwr.html\">drive.com.au</a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4795','2013-03-12 02:23:19','2013-03-12 02:23:19',NULL),(4802,'Parking ticket given to snow sculpture ','parking-ticket-given-to-snow-sculpture','Parking ticket given to snow sculpture ','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/snow-sculpture-car.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4803\" title=\"snow sculpture car\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/snow-sculpture-car.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"308\" /></a>\r\n\r\nTraffic wardens slipped up in Germany when they left a parking ticket - on a full-sized snow sculpture of a Volkswagen Beetle.Pranksters had built the car overnight in a no-parking zone in Aachen, complete with outlines for its headlights, windscreens and even the distinctive VW badge on the bonnet. For the full story please visit <a href=\"http://web.orange.co.uk/article/quirkies/Snow_sculpture_car_gets_parking_ticket\">http://web.orange.co.uk</a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4802','2013-03-20 02:42:46','2013-03-20 02:42:46',NULL),(4806,'Alonso and Massa in Ferrari 458 hot lap','alonso-and-massa-in-ferrari-458-hot-lap','Alonso and Massa in Ferrari 458 hot lap','<iframe width=\"590\" height=\"332\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/embed/bIaNgipAUz4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4806','2013-03-21 03:20:19','2013-03-21 03:20:19',NULL),(4810,'Collosion Repair Expo 2013','collosion-repair-expo-2013-2','Collosion Repair Expo 2013','<h2><a style=\"font-size: 16px;\" href=\"http://www.collisionrepair.com.au/visitor\"><img title=\"CRE2013\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/CRE2013.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"395\" /