ms.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone supplement items\" />\r\n\r\nAdd supplement/additional items to the quote. From the view page you can view the supplement quote and the original quote. When invoicing any supplements will be added to the original quote to give a grand total.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2009/07/crashzone-supplement-quote-example.jpg\" alt=\"Crashzone supplement qutoe example\" />\r\n\r\n* Supplementary images are sent to the original quote\r\n* Use the select image function in the view page when emailing the supp quote\r\n\r\nFor further information please contact support@crashzone.com.au',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=4825','2013-04-03 02:14:01','2013-04-03 02:14:01',NULL),(4829,'Crashzone National Conference 2013','crashzone-national-conference-2013','Crashzone National Conference 2013','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Collision-Repair-Expo.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4830\" title=\"Collision Repair Expo\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Collision-Repair-Expo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"94\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Crashzone National Conference 2013 </strong>on Saturday the 13/04/2013. Assembly will be <strong>4pm at the Collision Repair Expo</strong> <strong>our stand AD50</strong>. Depending on numbers we will head out for a BBQ or drinks at a local watering hole. This will be a chance to catch up with other Crashzone users and see where Crashzone is heading. Russ Hill from The River Group will be our host for the event. If you interested to come along please drop a quick email to me winston@crashzone.com.au so we can get some idea of numbers.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/CZ-conference.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4831\" title=\"CZ-conference\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/CZ-conference.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\