rts to PARTSCHECK\r\n13	PARTSCHECK when importing update the parts status i.e ORDER, RECEIVED and update cost price\r\n14	On the details page add Autotext field for Estimator, Body\r\n15	Invoice search should also look at deleted invoice\r\n16	IE10 drag and drop images\r\n17	Part page, view page should not show deleted item from ORM, Pnet\r\n18	Backup in Setting Page: Add Date From and Date To Option\r\n19	Backup in MYOB: Change wording \"from Date\" to \"Invoice From\"\r\n20	IE10: the update quote button does not work 100% in IE10 sometimes gets stuck saying updating\r\n21	XERO intergration: Imported invoice now will be imported as grand total\r\n22	XERO intergration: Separate Tax Invoice and Excess Invoice as two lines\r\n23	MYOB: Add Account Setting and use it when import into MYOB\r\n24	Time App: Reporting Page',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=5627','2014-01-03 00:54:54','2014-01-03 00:54:54',NULL),(5631,'BMW\'s hands-free drifting technology','bmws-hands-free-drifting-technology','BMW\'s hands-free drifting technology','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/BMW.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5633\" title=\"BMW\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/BMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"253\" /></a>\r\n\r\nBMW has changed the face of performance car driving with the unveiling of an advanced new autonomous driving assistant system that allows the driver to go hands off – not only in a straight line at constant highway speeds as with existing systems but also in extreme situations, including tyre churning burnouts and wild drifts around a race track. Good for P plate drivers. for the full story and video visit <a href=\"http://news.drive.com.au/drive/motor-news/bmws-handsfree-drifting-technology-20140107-30eey.html\">drive.com.au</a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=5631','2014-01-07 08:43:21','2014-01-07 08:43:21',NULL),(5637,'The new Audi Oven','the-new-audi-oven','The new Audi Oven','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/audi.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5638\" title=\"Audi\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/audi.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"267\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAll the doors locked themselves. I thought, \'That\'s not good\' ... I tried to wind the windows down and open the doors. When that didn\'t work I started to panic. For the full story visit<a href=\"http://news.drive.com.au/drive/motor-news/woman-locked-inside-audi-q3-on-41degree-day-20140108-30hde.html\"> drive.com.au</a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=5637','2014-01-09 04:03:51','2014-01-09 04:03:51',NULL),(5642,'Australia Day 2014 ','australia-day-2014','Australia Day 2014 ','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/cz-australia-day.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5643\" title=\"cz-australia-day\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/cz-australia-day.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"234\" height=\"76\" /></a>\r\n\r\nHappy Australia Day, hope everyone has a safe long weekend.',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=5642','2014-01-27 01:48:04','2014-01-27 01:48:04',NULL),(5650,'Lead-footers hit the highway in NT','lead-footers-hit-the-highway-in-nt','Lead-footers hit the highway in NT','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/no-speed-limit.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5651\" title=\"no speed limit\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/no-speed-limit.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"277\" /></a>\r\n\r\nNorthern Territory police have hit out at drivers who exceeded 200km/h during the first hours of a trial of open speed limits. For the full story please visit <a href=\"http://smh.drive.com.au/motor-news/leadfooters-hit-the-highway-in-nt-20140201-31trz.html\">smh.com.au</a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http