taining and resourceful event for anyone that can attend. This weekend is not about Crashzone but you the repairer and the industry we all work in. If you can make the effort to come along i am sure you will benefit from the information that is going to be on hand.\r\n\r\n<strong><em> </em></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Guest speakers include:</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Greg Preston ( industry wise man)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">**** ( third party specialist)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">David Taylor ( Parts Check)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Robin Taylor ( Axalta bench marking / lean process GURU)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Ben Cardy ( EZI METHODS, a web based alternative to other repair methods)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Winston O\'keefe ( Crashzone )\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Christiaan Hunter ( Autointegrity )\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Adam Martin ( Smash repairer )\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Russ Hill ( Smash repairer )</span>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Current schedule for the event below  (watch the forum for latest updates )</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Friday 28Th Feb at LAKESIDE Golf Club, Brisbane Rd Labrador</strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">9.45am. coffee and welcome (and payment) $20 for Crashzoners, $50 non Crashzoners.(covers both days)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">10am till 1pm GOLF , shot gun start, 9 holes. Cost would be $20 per head for golf, clubs and trolly.(separate)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1.00pm till 1.30pm . Subway platters. (included in price)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1.30 till 3.00pm. 90 minutes for CZ specific sessions- Up dates, Forum, Time App, Custom list, Reporting page, \"Other\" topics\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3.00 till 3.15pm afternoon tea (cheese platter in price)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3.15-4.45pm. CZ National Repair Network Launch &amp; AGM, followed by CZ GOLD proposal and FB discussion\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">4.45 pm close, few drinks at the Grand Hotel ( 5 minutes away on the broadwater)</span>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Saturday 1st March at OZ Trade ,11 Jay Gee Crt Nerang</strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n9.30, open, welcome and payment. $20 for Crashzoners, $50 non Crashzoners. (covers both days)\r\n9.30am\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">P</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">arts check  20 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Benchmarking LIGHT  15 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Benchmarking Heavy  40 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">10.45 till 11am- smoko, (platter in price)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">E-TIMES   20 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">WEB Based IDR 15 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">XERO,  OH&amp;S  10 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">12.30pm till 1pm. Lunch, Subway (in price)\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gavin McGahey   30 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">THIRD PARTY INFO,  30 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">How to win a job   30 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2.30-till 2.45pm afternoon tea platter in price\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Work dispute resolution   15 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">EZI methods   15 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Socialnomics, IT info  30 min\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3.45- 4.00pm. questionnaire and Close\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Quiet drink until tea.\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">6.30pm. Meet at Nerang Hinterland Hotel for meal. Any left over money goes on the bar.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://crashzone.wufoo.com/forms/crashzone-conference-registrat