ement qutoe example\" />\r\n\r\n* Supplementary images are sent to the original quote\r\n* In the view page use the drop down box to select the supp quote\r\n* Use the select image function in the view page when emailing the supp quote',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=6586','2015-04-13 01:13:09','2015-04-13 01:13:09',NULL),(6589,'Setting up EstImage for Crashzone','setting-up-estimage-for-crashzone','Setting up EstImage for Crashzone','<img src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/mini-front-end.jpg\" alt=\"Mini front end shot\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Process for setting up Estimage on Crashzone</strong>\r\n\r\n* Contact Stelvio to download and install the Estimage program to your computer\r\n* Estimage provides you with a user name and password to access their program\r\n* Once Estimage is installed you just need to add in the EstImage install path address that can be found in the setup section of the EstImage program.\r\n\r\nStelvio ( EstImage )\r\nPh: 02 9455 1055\r\nWebsite: <a href=\"https://www.estimage.com/MainWeb/login.jsp\">www.estimage.com</a>\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Crashzone Estimage user manual\" href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/crashzone-estimage-user-manual-20100719.pdf\">Crashzone Estimage user manual</a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=6589','2015-04-14 05:36:07','2015-04-14 05:36:07',NULL),(6591,'Crashzone group exercise - quote this car ','crashzone-group-exercise-quote-this-car','Crashzone group exercise - quote this car ','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/162TAV_0011.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6593\" title=\"162TAV_001\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/162TAV_0011.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"443\" /></a>\r\n\r\nIt\'s a mate of the shop owner, it\'s insured with a well known insurer and\r\nwill be assessed by a cert iv assessor, who is \"fair\"\r\n\r\nThere is no internal 