.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"158\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>You can add images to the quote using your email:</strong>\r\n\r\n* Open a new email\r\n* Type in you Crashzone email address ( find your CZ address in the settings )\r\n* Type the Crashzone quote number into the subject i.e ( 5013 )\r\n* Attach images to the email\r\n* Send email\r\n* Images will now attach to the quote  ( the process takes approx 1 minute )\r\n* Click on the details tab to refresh the system and load the new images\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/CZ11.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6648\" title=\"CZ1\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/CZ11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"275\" /></a>\r\n\r\nFor help with images please contact <a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/contact-us\">support@crashzone.com.au</a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=6645','2015-05-04 02:58:56','2015-05-04 02:59:17',NULL),(6651,'Crashzone how to export data','crashzone-how-to-export-data','Crashzone how to export data','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/accounting2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6652\" title=\"accounting2\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/accounting2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"211\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>How to export your invoices and job data from Crashzone:</strong>\r\n\r\n* Click on the settings link to access the settings page\r\n\r\n* Scroll down to the backup section in the settings page\r\n\r\n* Enter the  quote range or date range for the export\r\n\r\n* Click on “DATA” to generate the file\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/CZ-settings.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6653\" title=\"CZ settings\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/CZ-settings.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"506\" height=\"335\" /></a></div>\r\n<span st