ng authentic with a full racing wheel with uncompromising realism. You can check it out on the <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/284160\">steam store.</a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=6809','2015-08-20 07:09:11','2015-08-20 07:09:11',NULL),(6812,'Plane lightning strike ','plane-lightning-strike','Plane lightning strike ','<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HZVX921Z0wc\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=6812','2015-08-21 03:10:01','2015-08-21 03:10:38',NULL),(6816,'Crashzone system update ','crashzone-system-update-5','Crashzone system update ','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/CZ-logo.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6818\" title=\"CZ logo\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/CZ-logo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"128\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Crashzone system update:</strong>\r\n\r\nWe have uploaded a number of fixes to the system this week mainly around integration with ORM, PNET &amp; Estimage\r\nBelow is a list of the main points that have been updated.\r\n\r\n1 	Fixed: CZ Crash when sending Pnet Quote/Supp Quote caused by missing hrs\r\n2 	Fixed:CZ crash when sending manual quote (Missing Hrs in Others section)\r\n3 	Fixed: CZ can\'t import authorised message as Assessor put their comment in RR Section\r\n4 	Fixed: Pnet - Manual Quote required Hrs in Others Section ?\r\n5 	Fixed: CZ dont set 0.00 if ORM return report Item\r\n6 	Fixed: ORM- Use ORM rates in XML instead of rate from detail page\r\n7 	Disable Pnet Setup Setting - User need to email support@ to setup\r\n8 	Fixed: Pnet - submit quote but status still \"Draft\"\r\n9 	Fixed: Pnet - send updated request for quote customer cant send because status is not updated\r\n10 	 Fixed:ORM Get authorised into the wrong job caused same claim,rego, VehicleID\r\n11 	Fixed: ORM Get payment authorised 