/uploads/2016/03/Mercedes.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"336\" /></a>\r\n\r\nPOLICE in Victoria have taken delivery of the fastest, most powerful and most expensive highway patrol car to ever be put into service.Powered by a massive twin-turbocharged V8, the $200,000 Mercedes GLE63 AMG SUV coupe can reach the speed limit in just 4.2 seconds — quicker than any Holden Commodore or Ford Falcon pursuit sedan. For the full story please visit <a href=\"http://www.news.com.au/technology/innovation/motoring/victoria-police-have-australias-fastest-cop-car--a-200000-mercedes-gle63-amg-suv-coupe/news-story/04a395d1065f88514f2af6fc9118b841\">www.news.com.au</a>',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=6956','2016-03-16 02:55:08','2016-03-16 02:55:08',NULL),(6960,'KEN BLOCK\'S GYMKHANA EIGHT','ken-blocks-gymkhana-eight','KEN BLOCK\'S GYMKHANA EIGHT','<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_hf6ke1-i3E\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n\r\nHappy Friday everyone.',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=6960','2016-03-18 03:04:08','2016-03-18 03:04:08',NULL),(6965,'Happy Easter 2016','happy-easter-2016','Happy Easter 2016','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/easter-eggs.jpg\"><img title=\"easter-eggs\" src=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/easter-eggs.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"590\" height=\"286\" /></a>\r\n\r\nHappy Easter to the whole  Crashzone community, we hope you have a safe and wonderful Easter break. Best wishes from the Crashzone team.',0,0,2,'publish','open','http://www.crashzone.com.au/?p=6965','2016-03-24 04:02:27','2016-03-24 04:02:27',NULL),(6968,'Driver loses control of car, secures perfect parking spot','driver-loses-control-of-car-secures-perfect-parking-spot','Driver loses control of car, secures perfect parking spot','<a href=\"http://www.crashzone.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/bmw-parking.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-f